overview: Is there anything sexier than the dark side? In order to complete her Jedi training, Rey must master her lust - and not just for power! When Kylo Ren bombards her mind with sex soaked dreams, Rey knows she has to fuck him, or destroy him, once and for all! But is this dirty Jedi mind trick all a trap? or will Rey's first taste of RAW power drive her to the dicks of darkness?
title: Star Wars: The Last Temptation
